---
description: Apply project testing conventions including required Docker-based e2e gate.
globs:
  - "src/**/*.ts"
  - "tests/**/*.ts"
alwaysApply: false
---

- Follow TDD workflow where practical: failing test, implementation, refactor.
- Tests should verify behavior, not implementation details.
- Unit tests live under module `tests/` directories.
- E2E tests live in `tests/e2e/` and must be black-box.
- For feature-complete changes, ensure local Docker e2e execution is run and reported.
- If e2e fails, do not mark task complete; report failures with file and test names.
